# RRC Portfolio Dashboard

## Stack
- **Frontend**: Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS with Chart.js
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + SQLite (better-sqlite3)
- **Hosting**: Railway (auto-deploys from GitHub)

## Deployment
- Push to GitHub and Railway automatically redeploys. No manual deploy step needed.
- Railway uses a persistent Volume mounted at `/app/data` for the SQLite database.
- Environment variables (`ACCESS_PASSWORD`, `SESSION_SECRET`) are set in the Railway dashboard.

## Key Files
- `server/index.js` — Express server, API routes, auth middleware
- `server/database.js` — SQLite init, schema, seed data
- `server/excel-parser.js` — Budget Variance Report Excel parsing
- `app.js` — Client-side dashboard logic
- `index.html` — Main dashboard page
- `admin.html` — Admin page for uploads and property settings
- `styles.css` — Global styles (dark theme)
